headline: Is Dell Technologies (DELL) a Buy as Wall Street Analysts Look Optimistic?
summary: According to the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), one should invest in Dell Technologies (DELL). headline: Dell finance chief Yvonne McGill to resign
summary: Dell Technologies said on Monday its Chief Financial Officer Yvonne McGill would resign effective September 9. David Kennedy, senior vice president of Global Business Operations, will serve in the interim role, the PC maker said. The company also reaffirmed its third-quarter and full-year forecasts.

headline: Dell Technologies Announces CFO Transition
summary: ROUND ROCK, Texas, September 08, 2025--Dell Technologies (NYSE: DELL) today announces that Chief Financial Officer Yvonne McGill will step down from her role after a successful career at Dell that spanned nearly 30 years, effective Sept. 9, 2025.

headline: AI Data Center Company Evaluation Report 2025 | PowerEdge, ThinkSystem, and Networking Innovations Strengthen Market Leadership in Supporting Scalable AI Deployments Across Global Industries
summary: The AI Data Center Companies Quadrant provides an in-depth analysis of the global AI data center market, identifying key players and innovations. Evaluating over 100 companies, the quadrant highlights the top 17 market leaders, including Dell Inc., Hewlett Packard Enterprise, and Lenovo. AI data centers are crucial for industries needing high-performance computing for AI workloads. The report showcases trends like scalable infrastructure demand driven by generative AI and innovations in cooling
